part.content:
#!/bin/bash

groupadd bastion
useradd -d /home/bastion -r -g bastion bastion
mkdir -p /home/bastion/.ssh
touch /home/bastion/.ssh/authorized_keys

echo "" >> /home/bastion/.ssh/authorized_keys

chown -R bastion:bastion /home/bastion/
chmod 400 /home/bastion/.ssh/authorized_keys

cat <<EOD >> /etc/ssh/sshd_config 
Match Group bastion
   AllowAgentForwarding no
   AllowTcpForwarding yes
   X11Forwarding no
   PermitTunnel no
   GatewayPorts no
   ForceCommand echo 'This account can only be used for ProxyJump (ssh -J)'
EOD

systemctl restart sshd.service
